---
title: "onReport (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_pause: whenNotPaused modifier
    q_check_pause --> q_check_role: not paused
    q_check_pause --> q_revert_pause: paused
    q_revert_pause --> [*]: revert EnforcedPause()

    q_check_role --> q_extract_id: caller has FORWARDER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_revert_role: caller lacks FORWARDER_ROLE
    q_revert_role --> [*]: revert AccessControlUnauthorizedAccount()

    q_extract_id --> q_check_zero: workflowId = bytes32(metadata[0..32])
    q_check_zero --> q_check_allowlist: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()

    q_check_allowlist --> q_decode_report: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.contains(workflowId)
    q_check_allowlist --> q_revert_wf: not allowlisted
    q_revert_wf --> [*]: revert WorkflowIdNotAllowlisted(workflowId)

    q_decode_report --> q_extract_selector: (target, data) = abi.decode(report)
    q_extract_selector --> q_check_selector: selector = mload(add(data, 32))

    q_check_selector --> q_call: allowlistedSelectors[target].contains(selector)
    q_check_selector --> q_check_target: selector not in allowlist
    q_check_target --> q_revert_target: target not in allowlistedTargets
    q_revert_target --> [*]: revert TargetNotAllowlisted(workflowId, target)
    q_check_target --> q_revert_selector: target is allowlisted but selector is not
    q_revert_selector --> [*]: revert SelectorNotAllowlisted(workflowId, target, selector)

    q_call --> [*]: _call(target, data)

    note right of q_check_selector
        INV-001: selector check implies target is allowlisted (allowlistedSelectors is subset of allowlistedTargets)
        INV-002: only FORWARDER_ROLE can trigger external calls via _call
        INV-003: workflowId must be non-zero and present in s_allowlistedWorkflowIds
    end note

    note right of q_call
        INV-004: _call performs low-level call to target with data, inheriting WorkflowRouter msg.value
        INV-005: target + selector must both be explicitly allowlisted for the workflowId
    end note
